headline: Voya Corporate Leaders Trust Fund B Q4 2024 Commentary
summary: For the quarter, Voya Corporates Leaders Trust Fund Series B underperformed its benchmark, S&P 500 Index on a net asset value basis, primarily due to selection effects.
